{"id":6,"title":"About Laravel","author":"Linus Torvalds","text":"Laravel is a free, open-source PHP web framework, created by Taylor Otwell and intended for the development of web applications following the model\u2013view\u2013controller (MVC) architectural pattern. Some of the features of Laravel are a modular packaging system with a dedicated dependency manager, different ways for accessing relational databases, utilities that aid in application deployment and maintenance, and its orientation toward syntactic sugar.","unix":1459725802}